  "detailed_description": "<strong>UFOBIA</strong> is a first-person action horror adventure where police officers are called in to investigate an ongoing kidnapping in a abandoned mine.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Survive</strong> in the fight against beings from another planet.<br></li><li><strong>Explore</strong> the woods, villages and an abandoned mine for clues.<br></li><li><strong>Solve</strong> puzzles and find specific items to advance the investigation.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Everything is better with friends!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Invite</strong> your friends to help with the investigation.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927030/extras/e68d92443db208d949ae0b5b2dbbdb8d.poster.avif?t=1701936074\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927030/extras/e68d92443db208d949ae0b5b2dbbdb8d.webm?t=1701936074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927030/extras/e68d92443db208d949ae0b5b2dbbdb8d.mp4?t=1701936074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927030/extras/267b22306024fc6ad0d2a5956fedaf2d.poster.avif?t=1701936074\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927030/extras/267b22306024fc6ad0d2a5956fedaf2d.webm?t=1701936074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927030/extras/267b22306024fc6ad0d2a5956fedaf2d.mp4?t=1701936074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>UFOBIA</strong> is a first-person action horror adventure where police officers are called in to investigate an ongoing kidnapping in a abandoned mine.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Survive</strong> in the fight against beings from another planet.<br></li><li><strong>Explore</strong> the woods, villages and an abandoned mine for clues.<br></li><li><strong>Solve</strong> puzzles and find specific items to advance the investigation.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Everything is better with friends!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Invite</strong> your friends to help with the investigation.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927030/extras/e68d92443db208d949ae0b5b2dbbdb8d.poster.avif?t=1701936074\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927030/extras/e68d92443db208d949ae0b5b2dbbdb8d.webm?t=1701936074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927030/extras/e68d92443db208d949ae0b5b2dbbdb8d.mp4?t=1701936074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927030/extras/267b22306024fc6ad0d2a5956fedaf2d.poster.avif?t=1701936074\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927030/extras/267b22306024fc6ad0d2a5956fedaf2d.webm?t=1701936074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927030/extras/267b22306024fc6ad0d2a5956fedaf2d.mp4?t=1701936074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
